{"config":{"lang":["en"],"separator":"[\\s\\-]+","pipeline":["stopWordFilter"]},"docs":[{"location":"","title":"Zh-Plot: Show Chinese in Figures with one line code","text":""},{"location":"#_1","title":"\u652f\u6301\u7684\u6846\u67b6","text":"<ul> <li> matplotlib</li> <li> wordcloud</li> </ul>"},{"location":"#_2","title":"\u5feb\u901f\u5f00\u59cb","text":""},{"location":"#_3","title":"\u5b89\u88c5","text":"<p>\u4f7f\u7528 pip \u5b89\u88c5<code>zhplot</code>:</p> <pre><code>pip install zhplot\n</code></pre> <p>\u4f7f\u7528 uv \u5b89\u88c5<code>zhplot</code>:</p> <pre><code>uv add zhplot\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"#_4","title":"\u4f7f\u7528\u65b9\u6cd5","text":"<p>\u4f7f\u7528<code>zhplot</code>\u975e\u5e38\u7b80\u5355\uff0c\u53ea\u9700\u5728\u811a\u672c\u5f00\u5934\u5bfc\u5165\u5373\u53ef\uff1a <pre><code>+ import zhplot\nimport matplotlib.pyplot as plt\nimport wordcloud\n</code></pre></p> <p>\u5728\u6c49\u5316wordcloud\u7684\u65f6\u5019<code>import zhplot</code>\u9700\u8981\u5728\u524d\u9762: <pre><code>+ import zhplot\nimport wordcloud\n</code></pre></p>"},{"location":"#_5","title":"\u4e00\u4e2a\u7b80\u5355\u7684\u4f8b\u5b50","text":"<pre><code>import zhplot\nimport matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n\n\nplt.plot([1, 2, 3, 4])\nplt.title('\u8fd9\u662f\u4e00\u4e2a\u6807\u9898')\nplt.xlabel('\u6a2a\u5750\u6807')\nplt.ylabel('\u7eb5\u5750\u6807')\nplt.show()\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"#_6","title":"\u76f8\u4f3c\u9879\u76ee","text":"<ul> <li>japanize-matplotlib</li> <li>chineseize-matplotlib</li> </ul>"},{"location":"changelog/","title":"Changelog","text":""},{"location":"changelog/#unreleased","title":"[Unreleased]","text":""},{"location":"changelog/#020-2024-12-17","title":"[0.2.0] - 2024-12-17","text":""},{"location":"changelog/#added","title":"Added","text":"<ul> <li>Support chinese display in <code>wordcloud</code></li> </ul>"},{"location":"changelog/#011-2024-12-01","title":"[0.1.1] - 2024-12-01","text":""},{"location":"changelog/#changed","title":"Changed","text":"